## Description {#details}

This iterator provides a convenient way to iterate over the elements of an llvm.global&#95;ctors/llvm.global&#95;dtors instance.

The easiest way to get hold of instances of this class is to use the getConstructors/getDestructors functions.

Definition at line 51 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/executionengine/include/llvm/executionengine/orc/executionutils-h">ExecutionUtils.h</a>.
